        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Agency retainers run $10&ndash;30k/month. When you're pre-seed, that's your entire runway.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Too Rigid -->
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8B7FFF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Too Rigid</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Long contracts, limited revisions, waterfall process. Zero flexibility when your product is still changing weekly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Colater's Answer -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/[0.04] to-accent/[0.04] rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-8 md:p-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-animate>
