      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">One designer + six AI agents.<br>The agency model, reimagined.</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Fast</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">AI agents work 24/7. Your designer reviews daily. Most projects in 1&ndash;2 weeks.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Affordable</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Projects from $500. No massive retainers. Built for startup budgets.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Flexible</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Tight iteration loops. Continuous agent monitoring. Revisions are fast.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
